This product includes patterns and approaches informed by SaasMail
(https://github.com/choyiny/saasmail, Apache License 2.0) — particularly
around Cloudflare Email Workers inbound handling, MIME parsing, and
the rich-text composer. Where specific code is adapted, the source file
is noted in comments.

This product is designed to run as a plugin for EmDash CMS
(https://github.com/emdash-cms/emdash).
